com.sun.appserv.management.config
Interface ModuleLogLevelsConfig

All Superinterfaces:
AMX, AMXConfig, AMXMBeanLogging, ConfigElement, NotificationBroadcaster, NotificationEmitter, PropertiesAccess
public interface ModuleLogLevelsConfig
extends PropertiesAccess, ConfigElement

Configuration for the <module-log-levels> element. Values are those defined in LogLevelValues.

Constant Field Values
Method Detail

getAllLevels

Map<String,String> getAllLevels()
Get a Map keyed by Attribute name of all log levels. Attribute names correspond to the various get methods eg "Admin" for getAdmin(), "CMP" for getCMP(), etc.

The possible levels are as defined in LogLevelValues.

changeAll

void changeAll(String value)
Change all log levels to the specified value.

Parameters:
value - one of the values in LogLevelValues
